**Method 3: Pseudo-Elements (Most Control)**

```css
.swiss-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  position: relative;
}

.swiss-grid-item {
  position: relative;
  padding: var(--spacing-5);
}

.swiss-grid-item::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  width: 1px;
  height: 100%;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.swiss-grid-item::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 1px;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

/* Remove pseudo-elements on edges */
.swiss-grid-item:last-child::after {
  display: none;
}
